service postgresql start
service postgresql status

Default user for postgresql

sudo su postgres <- logs you in ubuntu with the username postgres
psql <-postgresql shell
\l <- displays all databases
\du <- displays all users
ALTER USER postgres WITH PASSWORD 'test123'; <- changes password for user postgres
CREATE USER user_1 WITH PASSWORD 'test123'; <- creates a new user
ALTER USER user_1 with SUPERUSER; <- adds a superuser role for user_1
DROP USER user_1; <- removes a user